{"tid":1403471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[以其人之道 還治其人之身]  黑 材 料 ！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-03T19:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:25:00.000Z","uid":296686,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"188cfed77f34947ed44afdc0f204c9c874b02322","tid":1403471,"uid":296686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:10:30.000Z","msg":"第一次開post。<br />\n<br />\n689話出一百萬懸賞掟國旗落海果位手足，想我地內訌，我諗諗下，呢招好有用！！！<br />\n<br />\n其實對以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">利益為首</span></strong></strong></span>既建制派、政府，用錢去分化佢地，係最實際有效既方法。<br />\n講真，政府<span style=\"color: red;\">表面團結，實質各懷鬼胎</span>，我相信某啲官員係有黑材料係手，但只係無誘因令佢地爆出黎。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地成立一個 黑材料眾籌，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">任何人都以匿名方式爆料！包括官員、建制派、警察、甚至係黑社會，都可以爆料！</span><br />\n然後將收集到既黑材料比哂所有傳媒or ICAC，包括紅底傳媒！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成立原因：<br />\n一，令政府、警察、建制內部人心惶惶，互相猜忌。<br />\n二，如果真係有猛料爆左出黎，絕對係呢場運動既突破點。<br />\n三，元朗單野，一定有人知內情，黑社會利益行頭，話唔定真係有人會爆料，到時警察一定收皮！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任何有關官、鄉、警、黑既黑材料（違法），或者係偷食既証據，每一則都可以換酬金！<br />\n<br />\n証據需求： 涉事人姓名、涉事事件、可以做得呈堂物供！單簡黎講，即係可以係法庭上作為証據！<br />\n<br />\n點解偷食都係黑材料：好似許志安咁，要佢知道佢自己係一個壞左既人，做人要專一，偷食係唔岩！<br />\n<br />\n暫時構思如下（要睇籌到幾多錢，每則黑材料）<br />\n警察：10萬（擒賊先擒王，總警司級別或以上）<br />\n鄉黑、建制：15萬<br />\n司長：30萬<br />\n特首：40萬<br />\n<br />\n如果黑材料令到涉事人坐監或辭職，double 酬金。<br />\n<br />\n唔敢做勇武，和理非都想出一分力，<br />\n呢個只係初步既構思，各位手足有咩諗法？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 純粹拋個idea，無能力做搞手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f45f9c8c160e9fc6b5804ca178de6502eab8f9","tid":1403471,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:12:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"09ca56dc3ab01b9f1ea082a9bdc2114eac81a15f","tid":1403471,"uid":296686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:18:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"fa12d380698e200648f77f203bead56d5e69e0c8","tid":1403471,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:18:55.000Z","msg":"但係搵到嘅料要fact check 唔係就變郭文貴，人地當你9up"},{"pid":"3483230d974db0fc31a095b13c743d082f87bf56","tid":1403471,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:19:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n有得諗"},{"pid":"fa9406031bc3de1b713ade753897144b5441e024","tid":1403471,"uid":205682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:21:29.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1882daf20ecdc816a573500e6bae425c72d53630","tid":1403471,"uid":296686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa12d380698e200648f77f203bead56d5e69e0c8","tid":1403471,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:18:55.000Z","msg":"但係搵到嘅料要fact check 唔係就變郭文貴，人地當你9up"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:22:11.000Z","msg":"所以我先話無能力做搞手，<br />\n呢個係需要一個團隊一齊去運作。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e02a45757c2a64bf70d8849d28e0ef0b6cc996c","tid":1403471,"uid":296686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:25:52.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1febf7639817d85152dbd19198ea29cee2739335","tid":1403471,"uid":296686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea9db487d1b38a48668642f675003470cb4471e2","tid":1403471,"uid":296686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces